OL,3,CCommonwealth Games 2030: Indian city
OL,4,Cof Ahmedabad confirmed as host
OL,6,FAhmedabad has been confirmed as the
OL,7,Fhost of the Commonwealth Games in 2030.
OL,9,FThe Indian city had already been
OL,10,Fselected over a rival bid from Abuja
OL,11,Fin Nigeria for the sporting event, but
OL,12,Ffinal approval was given at the
OL,13,FCommonwealth Sports' general assembly
OL,14,Fin Glasgow on Wednesday.
OL,16,FMoments after the announcement, 20
OL,17,FGarba dancers and 30 Indian dhol
OL,18,Fdrummers burst into the hall,
OL,19,Fsurprising delegates with a
OL,20,Fperformance.
