OL,3,CCommonwealth Games 2030: Indian city
OL,4,Cof Ahmedabad confirmed as host
OL,6,FThe news provides some long-term
OL,7,Fcertainty after the Commonwealth Games
OL,8,Fwere rocked in 2023 by the Australian
OL,9,Fstate of Victoria's decision to
OL,10,Fwithdraw as hosts of next year's games
OL,11,Fover rising costs.
OL,13,FGlasgow has since stepped in to host a
OL,14,Fslimmed-down version of the event.
OL,16,FDurban in South Africa was stripped of
OL,17,Fhosting rights for the 2022 edition
OL,18,Fafter failing to meet bid commitments,
OL,19,Fresulting in Birmingham taking over as
OL,20,Fhost.
