OL,3,CCommonwealth Games 2030: Indian city
OL,4,Cof Ahmedabad confirmed as host
OL,6,FThe Nigerian delegation at the general
OL,7,Fassembly in Glasgow congratulated
OL,8,FIndia on its successful bid and said
OL,9,Fit remains determined to become a
OL,10,Ffuture host itself.
OL,12,FCommonwealth Sport president Dr Donald
OL,13,FRukare maintains the movement has
OL,14,F"turned a positive corner" into a
OL,15,F"very solid" future following
OL,16,FAhmedabad's success.
OL,18,F"When we were in Singapore in '23,
OL,19,Fthere was a bit of a dark cloud with
OL,20,Fthe situation at that point," Dr
OL,21,FRukare said at a press conference.
