OL,6,F"We were very close to saying, 'What
OL,7,Fis the future of the Commonwealth
OL,8,Fmovement, Commonwealth sport?'
OL,10,F"But we are very happy that with the
OL,11,Fstepping up of Glasgow... that was a
OL,12,Fgame-changer."
OL,14,FHe continued, "This was also part of
OL,15,Four overall Games reset and refresh
OL,16,Fstrategy, which we had put in place as
OL,17,Fa board, where we are looking at the
OL,18,FGames in a slightly different way.
