OL,6,F"We have definitely turned a positive
OL,7,Fcorner, so we stand here looking very,
OL,8,Fvery optimistic that the future of the
OL,9,FGames and the movement is very solid
OL,10,Fand good.
OL,12,FThe President of the Commonwealth
OL,13,FGames Association of India, Dr PT
OL,14,FUsha, vowed that the games in 2030
OL,15,Fwill "lay the foundation for the next
OL,16,Fcentury".
