OL,6,FChief executive of the Commonwealth
OL,7,FGames Federation, Katie Sadler,
OL,8,Fbelieves that Glasgow played an
OL,9,F"absolutely vital" role in helping
OL,10,Fpush the movement forward with an
OL,11,F"innovative and different" approach to
OL,12,Fwhat will be the city's second time as
OL,13,Fhosts following the success of 2014.
